Fabricate gives you something other tools don't: the power to evaluate Clojure code to generate the contents of a page. The â€œusing Clojureâ€ part of that first sentence contains the core idea: Fabricate is built on the idea that you should be able to use Clojure to generate as much (or little) of your website as is necessary. 

